'''2016年馬其頓議會選舉'''原計劃於4月24日舉行<ref>[http://europa.eu/rapid/press-release_STATEMENT-15-5372_en.htm Statement by Commissioner Hahn and MEPs Vajgl, Howitt and Kukan: Agreement in Skopje to overcome political crisis] {{Wayback|url=http://europa.eu/rapid/press-release_STATEMENT-15-5372_en.htm |date=20160624000025 }} European Commission, 15 July 2015</ref>，後曾定於2016年6月5日<ref>[http://plusinfo.mk/vest/59131/pratenicite-od-vlasta-samite-kje-ja-otpovikaat-odlukata-za-24-april-izborite-na-5-juni Пратениците од власта самите ќе ја отповикаат одлуката за 24 април, изборите на 5 јуни] {{Wayback|url=http://plusinfo.mk/vest/59131/pratenicite-od-vlasta-samite-kje-ja-otpovikaat-odlukata-za-24-april-izborite-na-5-juni |date=20160329133739 }} Plus Info, 23 February 2016</ref>，到7月時宣布可能在2016年12月11日舉行<ref>[http://www.balkaneu.com/parties-fyrom-reach-agreement-elections-held-11-december/ Parties in FYROM reach an agreement, elections to be held on 11 December] {{Wayback|url=http://www.balkaneu.com/parties-fyrom-reach-agreement-elections-held-11-december/ |date=20160730052152 }} Independent Balkan News Agency, 21 July 2016</ref>，改選[[马其顿议会|索布拉尼]]所有123席。

==選舉制度==
索布拉尼的議席由全國六個選區以[[封閉式名單|封閉式名單]][[比例代表制|比例代表制]]各選出20名議員、席次分配使用[[漢狄法|漢狄法]]；另外有3席採用[[多數制|多數制]]以單議席選區選出分別代表歐洲和非洲、美洲與亞太區的海外馬其頓人<ref>[http://www.ipu.org/parline-e/reports/2313_B.htm Electoral system] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ipu.org/parline-e/reports/2313_B.htm |date=20160304061659 }} IPU</ref>。不過由於國外投票率過低，今屆代表海外僑民的議席出缺。

